n a posting board.  WHO ARE YOU PEOPLE??? come on, open up a bit!!! let's get to know one another!!! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFF0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bsaulttribe.showUserPublicProfile?gid=nativeonei>nativeonei</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#000000>(7/24/03 9:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fsaulttribefrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_smile.gif" align=absmiddle>  meeting members </span><hr size=1> this place is a good one to meet tribal members,but i don't have a lot of time <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCC0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bsaulttribe.showUserPublicProfile?gid=loberle@saulttribe>LOberle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#000000>(9/6/03 3:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fsaulttribefrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Reaching members</span><hr size=1> This is a good idea, although there are still many members who do not have direct access to computers. <br>
